Rating: 3
To the Chicago reader who couldn't find Sherry Vinegar: Green City Market. Any high-end grocery carries sherry vinegar, so you might want to scout around a little more. I have no trouble finding it in Toledo, Ohio, so I can't imagine that Chicago wouldn't have it!

